enazine, Thiothixene, Pimavanserin, Lumateperone, Olanzapine, Iloperidone, Triflupromazine, More', 'Tinidazole, Simeprevir, Rosuvastatin, Sulfadiazine, Lactic acid, Mitapivat, Methazolamide, Clindamycin, Ciclopirox, Darunavir, Probenecid, More', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/6269/', '[1] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0', 1767369485);
